Hi all

This is a list i compiled when building my handyboard. I found some parts
Quite hard to find and spent a lot of time reading through catalogs etc. So
i
thought it might save someone a lot of time. The list is pretty much
complete
and i now have a fully working handtboard but please double check it if your
gonna
order stuff using the part numbers in case of typos.


cheers Russ


